modShortDescription: Adds giant flying insects (can also be found in the Creature Pack) that give HONEY. Adds a prefab that you can find them in.
modDescription:
Adds giant flying insects (can also be found in the [Creature Pack](https://7daystodiemods.com/creature-packs-a-community-entity-project/)) that give HONEY. Adds a prefab that you can find them in.

You will need to copy the contents of modname/configs/Prefabs to gamefolder/data/Prefabs, otherwise you will get a nice NRE. If you can’t do that, please don’t ask for support, just stop using his mods. Easier on the old ticker.

**[Download](https://gitlab.com/guppycur/guppymods/-/archive/master/guppymods-master.zip?path=Guppycur%27s_Insects)**

The forum topic of the mod is [here](https://community.7daystodie.com/topic/9144-guppycurs-modlets/).

**Credits:** [Guppycur](https://7daystodiemods.com/tag/guppycur/)
